{"tid":1966364,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共軍及美軍軍機分別現身中華民國海域","createTime":"2020-04-10T06:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T07:03:03.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5c4be3e4141ce33a8962151537b1598bff1a3f27","tid":1966364,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T06:42:42.000Z","msg":"解放軍及美軍軍機分別現身台灣海域<br />\n10.04.2020 14:36<br />\n<br />\n執行遠海訓練的解放軍多架戰機，早上台灣西南方海域出現後，一架美軍偵察機，中午亦在台灣南部執行任務。台灣軍方強調，台海周邊海空情況，全程掌握。<br />\n<br />\n台方早上偵測到解放軍的轟-6、空警-500及殲-11等戰機，在台灣西南方海域執行遠海長航訓練，是解放軍戰機今年第6度現身台灣鄰近海域。他們經巴士海峽進入西太平洋，循原航路返回駐地，台灣派出空中偵巡戰機緊急升空攔截，並實施廣播驅離。另外，根據專門追蹤飛機動向的社交網站指，美軍一架RC-135U電子偵察機，接近中午時現身台灣南部海域，估計是監控解放軍的行動，是3月25日以來，美軍第6度在台灣周邊飛行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279963&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1279963%26csid%3D261_341&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi66bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=392db139\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279963&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"d48b8f5c6ab7ada787e01556e1f8081074f9df94","tid":1966364,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T07:03:03.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">【國際戰線，靠你支持！】</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: orange;\">頂住人民幣，對抗大外宣</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>為美國醫護捐贈醫療物資</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://charity.gofundme.com/o/en/campaign/masks-empowerment-campaign\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcharity.gofundme.com%2Fo%2Fen%2Fcampaign%2Fmasks-empowerment-campaign&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi66bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=3dcb3d8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ch